Rename or Move a Model

Change a modelâ€™s name or move it to a different app.

REQUIRED EDITIONS
Available in Salesforce Classic and Lightning Experience.
Available with CRM Analytics, which is available for an extra cost in Enterprise, Performance, and Unlimited Editions. Also available in Developer Edition.

To save a model:

From the Edit Model Toolbar, click the dropdown menu arrow, and then click Properties.
For App, optionally select a different app (such as a shared app).
For Model name, optionally specify a different name.
Click Save.

Einstein Discovery saves your model selections.
